articles.description: Jacob Gilyard scored 20 points, Nick Sherod had 17 and Richmond cruised to an 81-68 victory over Duquesne on Thursday night in the second round of the Atlantic 10 Conference Tournament.
articles.headline: Richmond cruised in 81-68 win over Duquesne in A10 2nd round

articles.description: Jaelan Sanford scored 21 points, Luke Knapke added 16 and Toledo advanced to the semifinals of the Mid-American Conference Tournament by edging Miami (Ohio) 71-69 on Thursday night.
articles.headline: Toledo survives scare, advances past Miami into MAC semis

articles.description: Duke's Marvin Bagley III is dominant in his postseason debut, scoring from all over the floor to give the Blue Devils a commanding lead.
articles.headline: Bagley does it all against Notre Dame

images.caption: Duke's Marvin Bagley III is dominant in his postseason debut, scoring from all over the floor to give the Blue Devils a commanding lead.
images.name: Bagley does it all against Notre Dame

articles.description: Jake Toolson scored 19 points, Connor Toolson added 18 and only missed one free throw between them as second-seeded Utah Valley scored 21 points at the line, defeating No. 7 seed Cal State Bakersfield 81-74 in a Western Athletic Conference Tournament...
articles.headline: Toolson brothers help Utah Valley top CSU Bakersfield 81-74

articles.description: Kyle Allman had 24 points and eight assists, Jackson Rowe added 18 points and Cal State Fullerton held off Long Beach State 76-74 on Thursday in a Big West Conference Tournament quarterfinal.
articles.headline: Cal State Fullerton edges Long Beach State 76-74 in Big West

articles.description: The Atlantic 10 Conference Tournament is a homecoming for Rhode Island senior guard Stanford Robinson and sophomore guard Jeff Dowtin.
articles.headline: No. 25 Rhode Island starts with VCU in A-10 tourney

videos.description: Brandon Key grabs a South Dakota missed shot and drives the length of the court then leaps for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Key goes all out for South Dakota St. and-1

videos.description: South Dakota's Matt Mooney steals the ball from the Jackrabbits and takes it the length of the floor before getting denied by Skyler Flatten.
videos.headline: Flatten swats away South Dakota shot attempt

videos.description: After a bad Jackrabbit turnover, Triston Simpson drives down the court but is stuffed by Tevin King who sprinted back on defense.
videos.headline: King stuffs South Dakota

videos.description: South Dakota's Matt Mooney takes the inbounds pass, drives down the court and drains a 3 while getting fouled. Mooney would make his free throw to complete the 4-point play.
videos.headline: Mooney's 4-point play keeps Coyotes in contention

videos.description: With under 2 minutes in regulation, David Jenkins Jr. sinks a 3-pointer to give South Dakota State a double-digit lead.
videos.headline: Jenkins' 3 helps seal the win for the Jackrabbits

videos.description: South Dakota State students storm the court as the Jackrabbits win the Summit League men's basketball championship and punch their ticket to the NCAA tournament.
videos.headline: Students storm the court as South Dakota State wins Summit League

videos.description: South Dakota State's Mike Daum reflects on his 25-point performance in the Summit Conference championship and speaks on his parents' strong influence on his career after getting a hug from mom.
videos.headline: A conference title means a hug from mom on camera
